      <title>德国投资者信心自六月以来首次上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/german-investor-confidence-increases-for-first-time-since-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预计借贷成本将比之前预期的更快下降，投资者对德国经济的信心四个月来首次增强。]]></description>
