      <title>欧洲官员称T+1过渡需要紧急努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/european-officials-say-t-1-transition-needs-urgent-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟监管机构周二表示，加快欧盟金融市场的发展应该成为当务之急，他们希望赶上大西洋彼岸的同行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/european-officials-say-t-1-transition-needs-urgent-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 09:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
