      <title>中国考虑以8530亿美元债务置换拯救地方政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-weighs-853-billion-debt-swap-to-rescue-local-governments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，中国正考虑允许地方政府在 2027 年前发行最多 6 万亿元人民币（8530 亿美元）的债券，主要用于再融资表外债务，这是政府提振世界第二大经济体计划的关键部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/china-weighs-853-billion-debt-swap-to-rescue-local-governments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 06:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市下跌，引发对市场前景的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/chinese-stocks-see-choppy-trade-as-investors-debate-next-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们再次怀疑北京的刺激计划是否足以支撑深陷通货紧缩和房地产危机的经济，中国股市大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/chinese-stocks-see-choppy-trade-as-investors-debate-next-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 02:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价暴跌拖累能源股，股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对以色列袭击伊朗能源设施的担忧有所缓解，原油价格大幅下跌拖累能源股，欧洲股市和美国期货小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称以色列不会针对伊朗原油，油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前有报道称以色列可能不会针对伊朗的原油基础设施，这缓解了人们对供应严重中断的担忧，而国际能源署预测明年市场将疲软，导致油价连续第三个交易日下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
